<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 75%), linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 75%);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-position: 0 0, 10px 10px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to {{companyName}}!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome to the future of learning, {{organizationName}}! ðŸŽ‰</h2>
        
        <p>This is a pivotal moment for your organization! You've just unlocked a platform that will transform how your team learns, grows, and succeeds. We're not just excited to have you aboard - we're honored to partner with you in creating a culture of continuous learning and excellence.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Why this matters for {{organizationName}}:</strong> In today's rapidly evolving world, organizations that invest in their people's growth don't just survive - they thrive. You've just given your team access to tools that will accelerate their development, boost engagement, and drive measurable results for your business.</p>
        
        <h3>Your roadmap to organizational learning excellence:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Explore your comprehensive organization dashboard and analytics</li>
            <li>Establish your first branch to start organizing your teams</li>
            <li>Invite your team members to join this learning revolution</li>
            <li>Design your first assessment and watch engagement soar</li>
            <li>Discover how data-driven insights will guide your training strategy</li>
            <li>Experience the ROI of investing in your people's potential</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Access Your Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        
        {{#if logoUrl}}
        <p><strong>Organization Logo:</strong> <a href="{{logoUrl}}">View Logo</a></p>
        {{/if}}
        
        {{#if website}}
        <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="{{website}}">{{website}}</a></p>
        {{/if}}
        
        <p>If you need any assistance getting started, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The {{companyName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to {{recipientEmail}}</p>
        <p>{{companyName}} | <a href="{{companyUrl}}">{{companyUrl}}</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 